{"chunk_id": "100state::0", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 0, "text": "## [page] https://100state.com\n\n![100state Coworking for Entrepreneurs](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxNDAwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjkzMyIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDE0MDAgOTMzIj48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+ \"100state Coworking for Entrepreneurs\")\nBook a Tour\n\n# Madison’s Friendliest Coworking & Entrepreneur's Space\n\nCoworking - Startups - Art - Community\n\n## Help us support United Way of Dane County\n\nDonate Now!\n\n### Coworking\n\nSupercharge your productivity in a workspace that feels like home in the heart of downtown Madison. We welcome entrepreneurs, remote workers, startup founders, solopreneurs, and creatives.\n\nMembership\n\n### Art\n\nUnleash your creativity at 100state. We proudly support Madison’s arts community with art exhibitions, twice yearly Gallery Night celebrations, and networking events.\n\n100arts\n\n### Entrepreneurship\n\nFounders Circle – Spark is an 8-week, high-energy bootcamp that launches aspiring entrepreneurs into the startup world with confidence and flair. Designed for beginners, this course covers the essentials of entrepreneurship — ideation, market validation, business modeling, and delivering a killer 30-second pitch.\n\n![Madison coworking space 100state main area](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDAwIiBoZWlnaHQ9Ijc1MCIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMDAgNzUwIj48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+)\n\n## The Space\n\nWelcome to your new favorite coworking space in Madison! Perched on the top floor of a charming vintage building, we’ve got 12-foot ceilings, tons of natural light, and walls bursting with local art. We get it—you didn’t sign up for a boring 9-to-5, so why settle for a stuffy office? Our office space is all about comfort and creativity, with an open layout that sparks cooperation and community, and of course, lightning-fast wifi.", "char_len": 1956, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "100state::1", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 1, "text": "tons of natural light, and walls bursting with local art. We get it—you didn’t sign up for a boring 9-to-5, so why settle for a stuffy office? Our office space is all about comfort and creativity, with an open layout that sparks cooperation and community, and of course, lightning-fast wifi.\n\nLocated one block off the Capitol Square in Madison, Wisconsin, we offer month-to-month all-inclusive memberships. Members choose between hot desks, dedicated desks, and private offices, and all have access to phone booths and reservable meeting rooms.\n\nNeed a private space for a quick call? We’ve got you covered with three conference rooms and a couple of cozy phone booths. Feeling podcast-y? Our podcast room/lounge is perfect for watching TV, napping, or recording your next hit show. And don’t worry about running out of steam—our kitchen is always stocked with coffee to keep you buzzing and blazing through your work.\n\n## The Community\n\nWhen you join the 100state family, you belong to a community of like-minded people who know you by name. Members often develop life-long friendships through shared lunches, ongoing events, and informal gatherings. We fulfill our mission to create a home for problem­ solvers, creatives, and entrepreneurs by providing startups a flexible workspace to host brainstorming sessions, hackathons, and team-building events. We also host community events such as educational talks, creative workshops, networking opportunities, and holiday socials.\n\n![Madison entrepreneur communty gathers in main coworking space](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDI0IiBoZWlnaHQ9Ijc2OCIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjQgNzY4Ij48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+)\n\n### Join a Thriving Community of Entrepreneurs in Madison\n\nJoin Now!\n\n### Upcoming Events\n\nNo event found!\n\n## A community of remote workers, solopreneurs, founders, creatives, problem solvers, and innovative thinkers.\n\n## Types of Membership\n\nWe offer multiple coworking membership levels to suit various work styles in our on-demand, flexible office space.\n\n#### Day Pass\n\nUse the space for one day during regular business hours (Monday through Friday, 9 a.m. to 5 p.m.). Must be booked in advance.\n\n#### Hot Desk", "char_len": 2283, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "100state::2", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 2, "text": "Types of Membership\n\nWe offer multiple coworking membership levels to suit various work styles in our on-demand, flexible office space.\n\n#### Day Pass\n\nUse the space for one day during regular business hours (Monday through Friday, 9 a.m. to 5 p.m.). Must be booked in advance.\n\n#### Hot Desk\n\nGet 24/7 access to the space and all amenities (printing, conference rooms, kitchen, events etc.). Sit at any available space in the open coworking area.\n\n#### Dedicated Desk\n\nRent a dedicated desk and get 24/7 access to the shared space and all amenities. Customize your desk with anything that boosts your productivity: monitors, ergonomic aids, personal items, etc.\n\n#### Private Office\n\nRent a private, lockable office for 1-4 team members to use. Get 24/7 access to the space and all amenities.\n\nLearn More About Membership\n\n![Our Madison coworking space has an amazing view of the State Capitol from our largest conference room.](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n### Private Meeting Spaces Available to Book on Liquid Space\n\nAccess to private meeting spaces is included at no extra charge in our office membership. Non-members can also book private meeting rooms to use as day offices or to host team-building events and client meetings.\n\nBook Now\n\n![Our coworking and entrepreneur space has reservable conference rooms](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## Membership Benefits\n\n*work*\n\n##### Coworking & Conference Rooms\n\n*school*\n\n##### Education & Mentorship\n\n*people*\n\n##### Connections & Networking\n\n##### Podcast & Recording Studio\n\n*trending\\_up*\n\n##### Brainstorming & Business Ideation\n\n*groups*\n\n##### Access to Member Only Events\n\n## Events and Programming\n\n### Public & Private Events\n\nMembers can host small gatherings for friends, clients, or colleagues outside of normal business hours in the shared space. Members also have the option to host paid programming in our 10-person conference room.", "char_len": 2284, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "100state::3", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 3, "text": "Access to Member Only Events\n\n## Events and Programming\n\n### Public & Private Events\n\nMembers can host small gatherings for friends, clients, or colleagues outside of normal business hours in the shared space. Members also have the option to host paid programming in our 10-person conference room.\n\n### Ongoing Community Events\n\nWe frequently host public events to promote community-building and professional development. We collaborate with outside speakers and other organizations for networking events, workshops, and classes.\n\n### Weekly Programming\n\nOur member-focused programming includes lunch-and-learns and happy hours.\n\n![Community members gather in our art-filled coworking space in Madison to play games.](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDI0IiBoZWlnaHQ9Ijc2OCIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjQgNzY4Ij48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+)\n\n# Our Partners\n\nNo results found.\n\n![Neider & Boucher](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n![Park Bank](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n![Wisconsin Technology Council](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## Testimonials\n\n“I’ve met a lot of people through 100state’s events who could support me and my endeavors. Whether that’s lawyers or accountants, graphic designers or marketers, so I am very grateful to have found my tribe at 100state.”\n\n![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxNTAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTUwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTUwIDE1MCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\nMaddy Niebauer\n\nCEO of Vchief", "char_len": 2195, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "100state::4", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 4, "text": "to have found my tribe at 100state.”\n\n![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxNTAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTUwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTUwIDE1MCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\nMaddy Niebauer\n\nCEO of Vchief\n\n“I really liked the diversity 100state embodies, you see that everyone is a trend breaker. We have raised a total of 5 million dollars, and when I first joined 100state we only raised 300k. A lot of that is contributed to having a professional looking space that I’m able to bring investors into and can be proud that I have an office here.”\n\n![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxNTAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTUwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTUwIDE1MCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\nJoy Tang\n\nCEO of Markable\n\nYou see members at 100state who are creating change in the community and forming a diverse workforce. Whether it’s by mentoring students or introducing them to entrepreneurship. They’re creating upward mobility for some of the most diverse companies in our community. I regard that as exemplary for 100state’s success.\n\n![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxNTAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTUwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTUwIDE1MCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\nMaurice Cheeks\n\n100state board of directors\n\n### Subscribe to our Newsletter!\n\n## [page] https://100state.com/cart\n\n## You may be interested in…\n\n## Your cart is currently empty!\n\n---\n\n## New in store\n\n* ![100state Logo Tee-You Do You](https://100state.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/38188-24-300x300.jpg)\n\n100state Logo Tee-You Do You\n\n$25.00 – $27.00Price range: $25.00 through $27.00\n\nSelect options\n* ![Cool Kitty 100state Logo Kiss-Cut Stickers](https://100state.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/45750-3-300x300.jpg)\n\nCool Kitty 100state Logo Kiss-Cut Stickers\n\n$3.00\n\nSelect options\n* ![Girls Who Code Tote Bag (AOP)](https://100state.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/45127-300x300.jpg)\n\nGirls Who Code Tote Bag (AOP)\n\n$24.00\n\nSelect options\n* ![Fries Before Guys Cotton Canvas Tote Bag](https://100state.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/101409-300x300.jpg)", "char_len": 2291, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "100state::5", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 5, "text": "options\n* ![Girls Who Code Tote Bag (AOP)](https://100state.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/45127-300x300.jpg)\n\nGirls Who Code Tote Bag (AOP)\n\n$24.00\n\nSelect options\n* ![Fries Before Guys Cotton Canvas Tote Bag](https://100state.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/101409-300x300.jpg)\n\nFries Before Guys Cotton Canvas Tote Bag\n\n$15.00\n\nSelect options\n\n## [page] https://100state.com/about-100state\n\n![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxNTAwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMDAiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxNTAwIDEwMDAiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4= \"20200603-IMG_3530\")\nabout us\n100state creates a community and home for problem­ solvers, creatives, and entrepreneurs. We inspire collaboration and create connections to unleash our community’s potential.\n\n### Our Story\n\n100state started with a back of the napkin business plan in 2012. More than a decade later we are still in business and have hosted and grown some of the area’s most successful startups, and provided a friendly and productive workspace for dozens of freelancers, remote workers, artists, and founders.\n\n### Our Mission\n\n100state’s mission is to empower and unite problem solvers, creatives, and entrepreneurs in a collaborative community dedicated to unleashing potential and driving innovation. As a nonprofit organization since June 7, 2013, we are committed to facilitating connections, inspiring collaboration, and creating opportunities through events, brainstorms, and an inspiring environment that addresses our community’s most pressing challenges\n\n## Our Vision\n\n#### We envision a community of change agents working together to create a new model of innovation that helps the world navigate the evolving human experience of the 21st century\n\n## The Team\n\n![Daniel G. Guerra Jr.](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## Daniel Guerra Jr.​\n\nExecutive Director", "char_len": 2093, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "100state::6", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 6, "text": "The Team\n\n![Daniel G. Guerra Jr.](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## Daniel Guerra Jr.​\n\nExecutive Director\n\n![Giovanni A. Aleman Sotelo](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## Giovanni A. Aleman Sotelo\n\nDeputy Director\n\n![Joseph Dahari](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## Joseph Dahari\n\nBoard of Directors\n\n![Nick Myers](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## Nick Myers\n\nBoard of Directors\n\n![Lou Elson](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## Lou Elson\n\nBoard of Directors\n\n![Andy Friske](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## Andy Friske\n\nBoard of Directors\n\n![Hector Gutierrez](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## Hector Gutierrez\n\nBoard of Directors\n\n![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## Abby Johnson\n\nBoard of Directors", "char_len": 2223, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "100state::7", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 7, "text": "Hector Gutierrez\n\nBoard of Directors\n\n![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## Abby Johnson\n\nBoard of Directors\n\n![Mushka](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## Mushka\n\nArt Director\n\n## [page] https://100state.com/core-values\n\n![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxNTAwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMDAiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxNTAwIDEwMDAiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4= \"untitled-20\")\ncore values\nThe things that make our community great.\n\n## We dream of a world where everyone follows their dreams and earns a living doing what they truly love to do.\n\n![100state values honesty](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n#### Appreciate Honesty\n\nExpect nothing less. Teamwork is hard, and communication is key. Even if it hurts, appreciate it.\n\n![Collaboration](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n#### Community\n\nThe people around us influence our lives. We recognize it, and so should you.\n\n![Be Positive](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1MzMiIGhlaWdodD0iNTMzIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTMzIDUzMyI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n#### Be Positive\n\nNegativity kills creativity. Everyone loves a positive person.\n\n![People First](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1ODQiIGhlaWdodD0iNTg0IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTg0IDU4NCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n#### People First", "char_len": 2287, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "100state::8", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 8, "text": "Everyone loves a positive person.\n\n![People First](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1ODQiIGhlaWdodD0iNTg0IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTg0IDU4NCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n#### People First\n\nPeople are what matter. When the right people come together, great things happen.\n\n![Win Win Win](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2NjciIGhlaWdodD0iNjY3IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjY3IDY2NyI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n#### Win Win Win\n\nTruly great projects benefit everyone. We look for that in every project we undertake.\n\n![Collaboration](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n#### Collaboration\n\nCollaboration creates value; competition divides it.\n\n![Trust](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0MjQiIGhlaWdodD0iNDI0IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNDI0IDQyNCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n#### Trust\n\nGood relationships are built on trust. 100state is built on relationships. Trust is key.\n\n![Be Courageous](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjAwIDYwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n#### Be Courageous\n\nFollow your passion. What ends up lasting and inspiring is what started with passion and courage.\n\n#### Anti­-Discrimination\n\n100state does not and shall not discriminate on the basis of race, color, religion (creed), gender, gender expression, age, national origin (ancestry), disability, marital status, sexual orientation, or military status, in any of its activities or operations. We are committed to providing an inclusive and welcoming environment for all members, staff, and visitors.\n\n#### Sharing Space", "char_len": 2130, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "100state::9", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 9, "text": "gender, gender expression, age, national origin (ancestry), disability, marital status, sexual orientation, or military status, in any of its activities or operations. We are committed to providing an inclusive and welcoming environment for all members, staff, and visitors.\n\n#### Sharing Space\n\nBe courteous when using the shared space. Be mindful of others, clean up after yourself, and consider others before booking conference rooms for excessive periods of time. In short, be a good roommate.\n\n#### Anti­-Harassment\n\n100state is committed to providing a workplace that is free from harassment. Harassment in the workplace is against the law and will not be tolerated. When 100state determines that an allegation of harassment is credible, we will take prompt and appropriate corrective action.\n\n#### Welcoming Guests\n\n100state members are welcome to bring guests to the space. If a guest intends to use the space on a regular basis for an extended period of time, invite them to apply for membership.\n\nWe’d love to have them!\n\n#### Sharing Ideas\n\n100state encourages sharing ideas freely, but acting upon others’ ideas in dishonest ways will never be tolerated. We are built on trust.\n\n#### Welcoming Guests\n\n100state members are welcome to bring guests to the space. If a guest intends to use the space on a regular basis for an extended period of time, invite them to apply for membership.\n\nWe’d love to have them!\n\n# As a 100state member, you agree to these values.\n\n## [page] https://100state.com/press\n\n![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxNDAwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjkzMyIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDE0MDAgOTMzIj48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+ \"untitled-13\")\n\npress\n\n![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxNDAwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjkzMyIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDE0MDAgOTMzIj48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+)\n\n# Press\n\nBeginning with our inception in 2013, 100state is covered in the press frequently. From the projects born in our space to our work in the community, these stories help strengthen our bond with the people of Madison.\n\nIf you are a reporter please contact us. Thank you for you support!\n\nContact Us", "char_len": 2289, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
