iIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)\n\n## So Cool Kitty 100state Logo Mug 15oz\n\n$20.00\n  Select options\n  This product has multiple variants. The options may be chosen on the product page\n\n## [page] https://100state.com/contact\n\n# Contact Us\n\n100state is a co-working space in Madison Wi, providing a community for entrepreneurs. Please contact us with any questions.", "char_len": 2275, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "100state::34", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 34, "text": "Mug 15oz\n\n$20.00\n  Select options\n  This product has multiple variants. The options may be chosen on the product page\n\n## [page] https://100state.com/contact\n\n# Contact Us\n\n100state is a co-working space in Madison Wi, providing a community for entrepreneurs. Please contact us with any questions.\n\nAre you interested in becoming a member?  Please learn more about it here.\n\n## 100state\n\n#### 17 S. Fairchild St. FL 7 Madison, WI 53703\n\n#### Support\n\n## [page] http://100state.com/membership\n\n![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxNTAwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMDAiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxNTAwIDEwMDAiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4= \"IMG_3538\")\nmembership\n\n## Questions About Becoming a Member?\n\nContact Us\n\n![Community Membership](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDI0IiBoZWlnaHQ9IjY4MyIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjQgNjgzIj48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+)\n\n## Coworking Membership\n\nCoworking spaces provide a collaborative and inspiring environment where entrepreneurs and small business owners can come together to share ideas, network, and grow their businesses and 100state is one of these magical places.\n\nOne of the biggest benefits of joining 100state is the ability to surround yourself with other startups, creatives, cool people and entrepreneurs. Being surrounded by other driven and ambitious individuals can be incredibly motivating and can help to keep you focused on your goals.\n\nAdditionally, 100state has a vibrant and supportive community where you can learn from your peers, share your successes and struggles, and gain valuable feedback on your business.\n\nOver the years our community attracts a diverse group of individuals, from freelancers and entrepreneurs to remote workers and small business owners and we’ve been part of some pretty amazing startup stories.\n\nThis diversity means that you’ll have the opportunity to connect with a wide range of people from different industries and backgrounds. You’ll be able to bounce ideas off of people with different perspectives, which can help you to see your business from a new angle.", "char_len": 2235, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "100state::35", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 35, "text": "amazing startup stories.\n\nThis diversity means that you’ll have the opportunity to connect with a wide range of people from different industries and backgrounds. You’ll be able to bounce ideas off of people with different perspectives, which can help you to see your business from a new angle.\n\nLast but not least, 100state host events, workshops, startup bootcamps, art galleries and provides countless networking opportunities. These events are great opportunities to learn from experts in your field, meet potential clients and partners, and connect with other entrepreneurs and small business owners.\n\n## 100state (Student) Members\n\n$100/month\n\nSame benefits as the Pro membership below, but full-time students will receive a $50/month discount on their membership as long as they are full-time students.\n\nBecome a Student Member\n\nIf you’d like to learn more, come down and cowork for a day (first time is our treat), and/or setup a tour, please email us at hello@100state.com.\n\n![student membership](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDI0IiBoZWlnaHQ9IjY4MyIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjQgNjgzIj48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+)\n\n![Coworking space with open tables and natural light](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDI0IiBoZWlnaHQ9IjY4MyIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjQgNjgzIj48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+)\n\n## 100state (Pro) Members\n\n$150/month\n\nThis is our most popular membership for someone who wants to be part of the 100state community. We’ll help connect you with other 100staters, whether you’re looking for personal or business connections, a new teammate for your startup, a mentor or advisor, or just want to get connected with a community of bright like-minded individuals", "char_len": 1877, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "100state::36", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 36, "text": "someone who wants to be part of the 100state community. We’ll help connect you with other 100staters, whether you’re looking for personal or business connections, a new teammate for your startup, a mentor or advisor, or just want to get connected with a community of bright like-minded individuals\n\nYou receive 24/7 access to the space and are encouraged to make yourself at home at 100state. Whether than means hosting events, gathering your startup team for a brainstorm, or leveraging the 100state community in a way to help drive value for your idea, startup or a social impact project. You get full use of our coworking hot desk and lounge areas, phone booths,and free access to our conference rooms, complimentary coffee every morning, can use 100state as your business address and much much more!\n\nBecome a Pro Member\n\nIf you’d like to learn more, come down and cowork for a day (first time is our treat), and/or setup a tour, please email us at hello@100state.com.\n\n## 100state Dedicated Desks\n\n$275/month\n\nYou get all of the benefits listed above for the regular (pro) membership +  a gorgeous workspace with locking file cabinet to call your own.\n\nThis is our most popular membership for remote workers and WFH’ers who want a consistent work area where they can come and go as they please. Leave your monitors and work station as you wish and it will be in the exact same place when you return.\n\nReserve Your Dedicated Desk (limited # available)\n\nIf you’d like to learn more, come down and cowork for a day (first time is our treat), and/or setup a tour, please email us at hello@100state.com.\n\n![Dedicated Desk Membership](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDI0IiBoZWlnaHQ9IjY4MyIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjQgNjgzIj48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+)\n\n![Medium conference room with natural light and a view of Madison's Capitol available for rent as a private office.](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDI0IiBoZWlnaHQ9Ijc2OCIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjQgNzY4Ij48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+)\n\n## Offices for Rent\n\n$850-$2,000/month", "char_len": 2231, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "100state::37", "doc_slug": "100state", "chunk_index": 37, "text": "for rent as a private office.](data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDI0IiBoZWlnaHQ9Ijc2OCIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjQgNzY4Ij48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+)\n\n## Offices for Rent\n\n$850-$2,000/month\n\nWant to be part of the vibrant 100state community but need or want a more private office space for you and your team?\n\nGood news, we also have opportunities to rent office space.\n\nPlease send us an email at hello@100state.com and we’d be happy to discuss helping you and your team evaluate 100state as a home for your startup and give you a tour of the space.\n\nIf you’d like to learn more, come down and cowork for a day (first time is our treat), and/or setup a tour, please email us at hello@100state.com.\n\n## Member Amenities\n\n### Office Services\n\nWe offer free printing, copying, scanning, and shredding. You can also receive business mail at 100state.\n\n### 24/7 Keycard Access\n\nMembers get 24/7 access to the shared space and can access all normal amenities at any time.\n\n### Coffee and Tea\n\nWe keep the pantry stocked with a variety of teas and provide a coffee maker for members to use. Our kitchenette includes a refrigerator, toaster oven, and microwave.\n\n### Reservable Meeting Rooms\n\nWe have several reservable conference rooms with whiteboards and projectors or TVs. Our largest conference room can accommodate 10 guests. Members can reserve these spaces for individual use or to meet with clients, partners, and colleagues.\n\n### Phone Booths\n\nOur shared space area includes two phone booths that offer privacy for phone calls and virtual meetings and keep the shared office quiet and productive for those around you.\n\n### Secure Indoor Bike Parking\n\nOur secure bike storage room is conveniently located next door to the main entrance. You don’t have to walk your bike through the halls or up the elevator or navigate any steps. Sudden rain storm? Leave your bike behind and pick it up later with 24/7 keycard access.\n\n## [page] http://100state.com/contact\n\n# Contact Us\n\n100state is a co-working space in Madison Wi, providing a community for entrepreneurs. Please contact us with any questions.\n\nAre you interested in becoming a member?  Please learn more about it here.\n\n## 100state", "char_len": 2289, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
