ing it easy to carry even with a week’s worth of shopping.\n\n.: 100% cotton canvas\n.: Heavy fabric (12 oz/yd² (406.9 g/m²))\n.: Sewn-in label\n\n## Additional information\n\n|  |  |\n| --- | --- |\n| Weight | N/A |\n\n## Reviews\n\nThere are no reviews yet.\n\nBe the first to review “Fries Before Guys Cotton Canvas Tote Bag” Cancel reply\n\nYou must be logged in to post a review.\n\n## Related products", "char_len": 2266, "id": 20, "source": "100state", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://100state.com/"}
