NT\nEND:VCALENDAR\n\n## [page] https://www.badgervc.com/events/spring-organization-fair\n\nBack to All Events\n\n# Spring Organization Fair\n\n* Tuesday, February 10, 2026\n* 5:00 PM\n\n8:00 PM\n\n* Kohl Center\n  601 West Dayton Street\n  Madison, WI, 53703\n  United States\n  (map)\n\n* Google Calendar\n\nICS\n\nSwing by the BadgerVC table at the Spring Org Fair! Meet our team, hear what we’re working on this semester, and learn how you can get involved.\n\nWe’re excited to meet you!", "char_len": 2276, "id": 16, "source": "BadgerVC", "type": "static_html", "category": "funding", "url": "https://www.badgervc.com/"}
