ison\\, WI\\,\n53715\\, United States\nEND:VEVENT\nEND:VCALENDAR\n\n## [page] https://www.badgervc.com/events/applications-have-opened\n\nBack to All Events\n\n# Applications are Open\n\n* Friday, January 30, 2026\n* 8:00 AM\n\n8:01 AM\n\n* Google Calendar\n\nICS\n\nApplications for BadgerVC Spring Membership will open on the evening of Thursday, January 29th.\n\nApplications will close on February 11th.\n\nPlease reach out to badgervc@gmail.com with any questions regarding applications!\n\nPrevious\n\nPrevious", "char_len": 2291, "id": 16, "source": "BadgerVC", "type": "static_html", "category": "funding", "url": "https://www.badgervc.com/"}
