am - 12:00pm\n\nJoin Max Lynch (co-founder of Ionic, whose open source mobile frameworks have shaped how millions of developers build apps before its 2022 acquisition by OutSystems) and Meghan Gaffney (who took Veda from concept to acquisition, raising $50M+ and building a landmark healthcare AI patent portfolio) for a conversation on what it takes to go from formation to exit. Moderated by Scott Resnick.\n\n## inside the deal\n\nDreambank\n\nMay 14th, 1:00pm - 1:45pm", "char_len": 2257, "id": 19, "source": "Capital Entrepreneurs", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://capitalentrepreneurs.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "capital-entrepreneurs::5", "doc_slug": "capital-entrepreneurs", "chunk_index": 5, "text": "by OutSystems) and Meghan Gaffney (who took Veda from concept to acquisition, raising $50M+ and building a landmark healthcare AI patent portfolio) for a conversation on what it takes to go from formation to exit. Moderated by Scott Resnick.\n\n## inside the deal\n\nDreambank\n\nMay 14th, 1:00pm - 1:45pm\n\nJoin Jon Horne (Managing Director of Idea Fund) along with their portfolio CEO, Nick Amundsen of Insuraviews, to take a peek behind the curtain and learn how they went from intro, to pitch, to term sheet and company-long partnership. Moderated by Taralinda Willis.\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/UrM4PBovOMQugqE5B0nv6e1JOiM.jpg?width=6240&height=4160)\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/piDSJ5Za6JXLb65qNX3YSqiWhE.png?width=2880&height=1622)\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/piDSJ5Za6JXLb65qNX3YSqiWhE.png?width=2880&height=1622)\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/G8tGpy4hCh6sfvSpPXnQ68MISY.jpg?width=1860&height=480)\n\n## Pitch Competition\n\nDreambank\n\nMay 14th, 2:00pm - 3:15pm\n\nIf youâre thinking of fundraising in the next year, this is perfect for you and your company.\n\nð¥ **Compete for $5,000 cash**\n\nð¤ **Showcase your startup**\n\nð **Get honest feedback from investors & founders**\n\nApply to compete\n\n## Pitches That Worked\n\nStartingBlock\n\nMay 14th, 3:15pm - 4:15pm\n\nA behind-the-scenes look at real investor pitches. NOT a competitionâthis is a learning session.\n\nLive Pitch Demonstrations â See how successful founders pitch. What worked, what didnât, and why.\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/wFBg02ABxhA0mWgmeyEJfkh2oe0.png?width=2758&height=1600)\n\n\"Founder Day connected me with founders who truly understand the challenges of building something from the ground up. The conversations were real, the connections meaningful, and I left energized with fresh ideas to move my business forward.\"\n\n### Olivia Wisden\n\n###### CEO Underbelly\n\n\"Founder Day was a game-changer. It gave me the perfect space to share UnderBellyâs work and connect with new clients who truly resonated with our vision. Invaluable connections, incredible energyâ100% worth it!\"\n\n### Olivia Wisden\n\n###### CEO Underbelly", "char_len": 2163, "id": 19, "source": "Capital Entrepreneurs", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://capitalentrepreneurs.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "capital-entrepreneurs::6", "doc_slug": "capital-entrepreneurs", "chunk_index": 6, "text": "Olivia Wisden\n\n###### CEO Underbelly\n\n\"Founder Day was a game-changer. It gave me the perfect space to share UnderBellyâs work and connect with new clients who truly resonated with our vision. Invaluable connections, incredible energyâ100% worth it!\"\n\n### Olivia Wisden\n\n###### CEO Underbelly\n\n\"Founder Day connected me with founders who truly understand the challenges of building something from the ground up. The conversations were real, the connections meaningful, and I left energized with fresh ideas to move my business forward.\"\n\n### Olivia Wisden\n\n###### CEO Underbelly\n\n## tickets\n\n###### Open Mic NIght\n\nFree\n\n20 Founders, 60s Pitches\n\nFree food and drinks\n\nGrab your ticket\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/szY2WFOYz7UPa7QypyyNkKwiU.svg?width=12&height=25)\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/szY2WFOYz7UPa7QypyyNkKwiU.svg?width=12&height=25)\n\n###### Open Mic NIght\n\nFree\n\n20 Founders, 60s Pitches\n\nFree food and drinks\n\nReserve Ticket\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/szY2WFOYz7UPa7QypyyNkKwiU.svg?width=12&height=25)\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/szY2WFOYz7UPa7QypyyNkKwiU.svg?width=12&height=25)\n\n###### Founder Day\n\nFree\n\nFull day of events!\n\nPitches, Talks, and Networking\n\nGrab your ticket\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/szY2WFOYz7UPa7QypyyNkKwiU.svg?width=12&height=25)\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/szY2WFOYz7UPa7QypyyNkKwiU.svg?width=12&height=25)\n\n###### Founder Day\n\nFree\n\nFull day of events!\n\nPitches, Talks, and Networking\n\nReserve Ticket\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/szY2WFOYz7UPa7QypyyNkKwiU.svg?width=12&height=25)\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/szY2WFOYz7UPa7QypyyNkKwiU.svg?width=12&height=25)\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/N2iH8gM7sc3YAY5c10NKpxr5Yc.svg?width=24&height=25)\n\n![](https: