{"chunk_id": "capital-entrepreneurs::7", "doc_slug": "capital-entrepreneurs", "chunk_index": 7, "text": "Got questions?\n\nFind answers to common questions about the event, including event times, parking information, and accommodation options.\n\nWhat are the event times?\n\nOpen Mic Night:\nMay 14th 6:30pm - 9:30pm.\n\nFounder Day:\nMay 15th 10:00am - 4:00pm.\n\nIs parking available?\n\nThere are a few parking garages near the venues (recommended).\n\nYou can also find street parking, but BE CAUTIOUS! Read the sign before you park. Many blocks have slightly different rules and they will ticket you. E Washington Ave will tow your car from 3p-6p!\n\nAre there accommodation options?\n\nYes, we have partnered with several nearby hotels to offer special rates for attendees. Details on recommended accommodations and booking links will be provided upon registration.\n\nHow can I register for updates?\n\nNot ready to register for the event, but still want updates? Subscribe to our event newsletter.\n\nIs there a registration fee?\n\nThanks to American Family Insurance DreamBank, the event is FREE!\n\nHowever, you must register to get in, and you must let us know if you are know longer coming.\n\nHow can I become a sponsor?\n\nIf you would like to support the event, please see our sponsorship form. This will show you a menu of what is available and actions on next steps.\n\nWho's invited?\n\nStartups are invited! Weâd love to see founders and startup leaders join us. If youâre a service provider, we encourage attending through sponsorship to best engage with the community. Thanks!\n\nWhat are the event times?\n\nOpen Mic Night:\nMay 14th 6:30pm - 9:30pm.\n\nFounder Day:\nMay 15th 10:00am - 4:00pm.\n\nIs parking available?\n\nThere are a few parking garages near the venues (recommended).\n\nYou can also find street parking, but BE CAUTIOUS! Read the sign before you park. Many blocks have slightly different rules and they will ticket you. E Washington Ave will tow your car from 3p-6p!\n\nAre there accommodation options?\n\nYes, we have partnered with several nearby hotels to offer special rates for attendees. Details on recommended accommodations and booking links will be provided upon registration.\n\nHow can I register for updates?\n\nNot ready to register for the event, but still want updates? Subscribe to our event newsletter.\n\nIs there a registration fee?", "char_len": 2231, "id": 19, "source": "Capital Entrepreneurs", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://capitalentrepreneurs.com/"}
{"chunk_id": "capital-entrepreneurs::8", "doc_slug": "capital-entrepreneurs", "chunk_index": 8, "text": "hotels to offer special rates for attendees. Details on recommended accommodations and booking links will be provided upon registration.\n\nHow can I register for updates?\n\nNot ready to register for the event, but still want updates? Subscribe to our event newsletter.\n\nIs there a registration fee?\n\nThanks to American Family Insurance DreamBank, the event is FREE!\n\nHowever, you must register to get in, and you must let us know if you are know longer coming.\n\nHow can I become a sponsor?\n\nIf you would like to support the event, please see our sponsorship form. This will show you a menu of what is available and actions on next steps.\n\nWho's invited?\n\nStartups are invited! Weâd love to see founders and startup leaders join us. If youâre a service provider, we encourage attending through sponsorship to best engage with the community. Thanks!\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/sPLMXnNkXQhdkY1KI6DhEFPs.png?width=637&height=751)\n\n## OUR Sponsors\n\n## OUR Sponsors\n\nWant to support the event?\n\nContact us\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/tv0YKCmyGBWFGXu1s0J6790anio.jpg?width=2050&height=344)\n\n#### StartingBlock\n\nJoin a community of entrepreneurs, startups, and remote workers at StartingBlock, where you'll have access to resources, mentorship, and a collaborative coworking workspace. With 50,000 sq ft of space in Madison's Capitol East neighborhood, StartingBlock is the perfect place to launch your business or run business as usual.\n\nLearn More\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/w4ALsc7GDE6LYdV1nsXaxAybBI.png?width=1920&height=1080)\n\n#### DreamBank\n\nThe American Family Insurance DreamBank offers a vibrant community of events, resources and connections designed to help people pursue and protect their most valuable asset â their dreams.â¯â¯\n\nLearn More\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/G8tGpy4hCh6sfvSpPXnQ68MISY.jpg?width=1860&height=480)\n\n#### WEDC\n\nWEDCâs Entrepreneurship & Innovation (E&I) is fueling start ups and innovation to power Wisconsin forward by building density in entrepreneurial ecosystems and supporting high-growth ventures with funding, resources, and strategic partnerships.\n\nLearn More\n\n![](https://framerusercontent.com/images/GF7l0tpHXQ0T5WQsffM5Bik0NQ.png?width=240&height=236)\n\n### IdeaFund", "char_len": 2271, "id": 19, "source": "Capital Entrepreneurs", "type": "static_html", "category": "community", "url": "https://capitalentrepreneurs.com/"}
