may check out this kit for multiple days outside of the lab, contact the Shop Manager.\n\n## Links + Useful Info", "char_len": 1924, "id": 10, "source": "Grainger Engineering Design Innovation Lab", "type": "static_html", "category": "makerspace", "url": "https://making.engr.wisc.edu/"}
