what a professor is.\n\nAnd so they saw me on the computer a lot and they're like, \"Oh, like you know, you know, when we order stuff online, like that's you that's what the computer is for.\" That's when they were involved in the computer.\n\nAnd so that basically was online shopping.\n\nThat's how distant they were from this this occupation.", "char_len": 2150, "id": 23, "source": "Student founder podcast transcripts", "type": "transcript", "category": "transcript", "url": "file://jon-eckhardt-startup-wisconsin.txt"}
