e numbers and the stats and what does success really look like?\n\n>> Yeah, >> for me it's the increasing number of companies formed that are affiliated with the university that are created by some some act because of of WMadison and also increasing quality of these efforts.", "char_len": 2080, "id": 23, "source": "Student founder podcast transcripts", "type": "transcript", "category": "transcript", "url": "file://jon-eckhardt-startup-wisconsin.txt"}
