g this course in person with others is very edifying, and I think those insights and discussions were invaluable!\n>\n> —Tracey Mac Murchy, Dimension IV Madison Design Group, 2024 Participant", "char_len": 2056, "id": 8, "source": "SBDC UW-Madison", "type": "static_html", "category": "business-support", "url": "https://sbdc.wisc.edu/"}
