ip potential! Would definitely recommend it to anyone interested in growing as a leader.”\n>\n> —Hamdi Munishi, Quality Manager Automation Components, Inc.\n\n> I enjoyed the opportunity to be introspective and examine how I can tailor my leadership/coaching strategies to my unique strengths.\n>\n> —Account Executive, FINN Partners, Summer 2025 Participant\n\n## Instructor\n\n###\n\n###\n\n### **SARAH SMYRK, MA, CLF®, RCC™, CCMP®**", "char_len": 2288, "id": 8, "source": "SBDC UW-Madison", "type": "static_html", "category": "business-support", "url": "https://sbdc.wisc.edu/"}
