{"chunk_id": "starting-block-madison::36", "doc_slug": "starting-block-madison", "chunk_index": 36, "text": "11 | AMY CALDER\n\nCRM 101\n\n![Nikki Bown Headshot](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_36c7af524fc840c49cb80d1066e00d53~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_287,h_287,fp_0.5_0.44,q_75,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_36c7af524fc840c49cb80d1066e00d53~mv2.png)\n\nMARCH 27 | NIKKI BOWN\n\nUtilizing Zapier in Your Business\n\n![Eagan Heath Headshot](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_7462f013ee45438d95dd358b47b09565~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_287,h_287,fp_0.48_0.35,q_75,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_7462f013ee45438d95dd358b47b09565~mv2.png)\n\nAPRIL 11 | EAGAN HEATH\n\nHow to Use Google Ads for Leads & Sales\n\n![James Phetteplace Headshot](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_752a335eb7e54ffaab39f076d7ebe26f~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_288,h_287,fp_0.41_0.35,q_75,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_752a335eb7e54ffaab39f076d7ebe26f~mv2.png)\n\nMAY 6 | JAMES PHETTEPLACE\n\nUnderstanding SEO Basics\n\n![Phil Ouellette Headshot](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_bb22d2c6a7be4ee8a1793f9df2d0cb2e~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_287,h_287,fp_0.5_0.48,q_75,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_bb22d2c6a7be4ee8a1793f9df2d0cb2e~mv2.png)\n\nJUNE 5 | PHIL OUELLETTE\n\nEntrepreneurial Operating System (OES) IMPLEMENTATION\n\n## [page] https://www.startingblockmadison.org/event-spaces\n\n# Services\n\nProviding Everything You Need\n\n![20221221_072221_50028A.jpeg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_5b5ccfffee89435fbb521937d86d87e1~mv2.jpeg/v1/fill/w_83,h_62,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_5b5ccfffee89435fbb521937d86d87e1~mv2.jpeg)\n\n# Host Your Event\n\n### Elevate your event experience at StartingBlock.\n\nDOWNLOAD OUR RATE SHEET\n\n###### Whether you're a member or not, StartingBlock's event space is the perfect venue for your next gathering. With a stunning view of the Capitol East neighborhood from our 3rd-floor cafe, your guests will be impressed from the moment they arrive. Plus, our flexible space can accommodate events of all sizes and types.\n\nINQUIRE NOW\n\nAnchor 1\n\n![VI6A2980-scaled.jpg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_8c44c23206d54e57be58e3ae6808f658~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_122,h_81,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_8c44c23206d54e57be58e3ae6808f658~mv2.jpg)\n\n### Conference Rooms\n\n10-20 GUESTS  •  3 ROOMS AVAILABLE", "char_len": 2235, "id": 17, "source": "StartingBlock Madison", "type": "static_html", "category": "accelerator", "url": "https://www.startingblockmadison.org/"}
{"chunk_id": "starting-block-madison::37", "doc_slug": "starting-block-madison", "chunk_index": 37, "text": "1\n\n![VI6A2980-scaled.jpg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_8c44c23206d54e57be58e3ae6808f658~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_122,h_81,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_8c44c23206d54e57be58e3ae6808f658~mv2.jpg)\n\n### Conference Rooms\n\n10-20 GUESTS  •  3 ROOMS AVAILABLE\n\nTired of boring meeting spaces? Elevate your next meeting at StartingBlock Event Space. Our 3 conference rooms can comfortably seat between 10 and 20 people and are perfect for board or staff meetings.\n\nBOOK NOW\n\n### Classroom\n\nUP TO 45 GUESTS\n\nWhether you're hosting a workshop, conference, or networking event, our Classroom (previously Digital Den) can be configured to fit your needs and accommodate up to 45 guests.\n\nINQUIRE NOW\n\n![DSC00475.JPG](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_de8e8f00a0324ceab948f37f2042698b~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_122,h_81,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_de8e8f00a0324ceab948f37f2042698b~mv2.jpg)\n\n![startingblock-madison-am-fam-cafe.jpg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_91e22c683c29402cbabf4ea79f7a2a9d~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_122,h_69,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_91e22c683c29402cbabf4ea79f7a2a9d~mv2.jpg)\n\n### Café\n\nUP TO 140 GUESTS\n\nImpress your guests with panoramic views of the Capitol East neighborhood from our 3rd Floor Cafe. With seating for up to 140, it's the perfect space for your next event.\n\nINQUIRE NOW\n\n### Media Studio\n\nPODCAST, PHOTO, AND VIDEO SPACE\n\nOur podcast studio is configured for all your content creation needs. It is equipped with a green screen, a seamless white backdrop and sound deadening baffles.  All you need to bring is your video and sound equipment.\n\nINQUIRE NOW\n\n![DSC00448.JPG](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_73fcaa82defb4c4a92c31b932fa0c247~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_122,h_81,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_73fcaa82defb4c4a92c31b932fa0c247~mv2.jpg)\n\n## [page] https://www.startingblockmadison.org/event-spaces-meetings\n\n# Services\n\nProviding Everything You Need\n\n![20221221_072221_50028A.jpeg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_5b5ccfffee89435fbb521937d86d87e1~mv2.jpeg/v1/fill/w_83,h_62,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_5b5ccfffee89435fbb521937d86d87e1~mv2.jpeg)", "char_len": 2282, "id": 17, "source": "StartingBlock Madison", "type": "static_html", "category": "accelerator", "url": "https://www.startingblockmadison.org/"}
{"chunk_id": "starting-block-madison::38", "doc_slug": "starting-block-madison", "chunk_index": 38, "text": "Services\n\nProviding Everything You Need\n\n![20221221_072221_50028A.jpeg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_5b5ccfffee89435fbb521937d86d87e1~mv2.jpeg/v1/fill/w_83,h_62,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_5b5ccfffee89435fbb521937d86d87e1~mv2.jpeg)\n\n# Host Your Meeting\n\n### Elevate your meeting experience at StartingBlock.\n\nDOWNLOAD OUR RATE SHEET\n\nOur meeting spaces are designed to meet your needs, whether you're small team or a large group. Equipped with modern amenities, you can concentrate on your presentation while we take care of the rest. Reserve your space now and take your meetings to the next level.\n\n![VI6A2980-scaled.jpg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_8c44c23206d54e57be58e3ae6808f658~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_122,h_81,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_8c44c23206d54e57be58e3ae6808f658~mv2.jpg)\n\n### Conference Rooms\n\n10-20 GUESTS  •  3 ROOMS AVAILABLE\n\nTired of boring meeting spaces? Elevate your next meeting at StartingBlock Event Space. Our 3 conference rooms can comfortably seat between 10 and 20 people and are perfect for board or staff meetings.\n\nBOOK NOW\n\n![DSC00475.JPG](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_de8e8f00a0324ceab948f37f2042698b~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_121,h_81,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_de8e8f00a0324ceab948f37f2042698b~mv2.jpg)\n\n### Classroom\n\nUP TO 45 GUESTS\n\nWhether you're hosting a workshop, conference, or networking event, our classroom can be configured to fit your needs and accommodate up to 45 guests.\n\nINQUIRE NOW\n\n![DSC00475.JPG](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_de8e8f00a0324ceab948f37f2042698b~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_122,h_82,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_de8e8f00a0324ceab948f37f2042698b~mv2.jpg)\n\n![DSC00448.JPG](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_73fcaa82defb4c4a92c31b932fa0c247~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_122,h_81,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_73fcaa82defb4c4a92c31b932fa0c247~mv2.jpg)\n\n### Media Studio\n\nPODCAST, PHOTO, AND VIDEO SPACE", "char_len": 2079, "id": 17, "source": "StartingBlock Madison", "type": "static_html", "category": "accelerator", "url": "https://www.startingblockmadison.org/"}
{"chunk_id": "starting-block-madison::39", "doc_slug": "starting-block-madison", "chunk_index": 39, "text": "Media Studio\n\nPODCAST, PHOTO, AND VIDEO SPACE\n\nOur media studio is configured for all your content creation needs. It is equipped with a green screen, a seamless white backdrop and sound deadening baffles.  All you need to bring is your video and sound equipment.\n\nINQUIRE NOW\n\n## [page] https://www.startingblockmadison.org/event-spaces-events\n\n# Services\n\nProviding Everything You Need\n\n![20221221_072221_50028A.jpeg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_5b5ccfffee89435fbb521937d86d87e1~mv2.jpeg/v1/fill/w_83,h_62,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_5b5ccfffee89435fbb521937d86d87e1~mv2.jpeg)\n\n# Host Your Event\n\n### Elevate your event experience at StartingBlock.\n\nDOWNLOAD OUR RATE SHEET\n\n# About\n\n###### Whether you're a member or not, StartingBlock's event spaces are the perfect venue for your next gathering. With a stunning view of the Capitol East neighborhood from our 3rd floor Work Café, your guests will be impressed from the moment they arrive. Plus, our flexible space can accommodate events of all sizes and types.\n\n![startingblock-madison-am-fam-cafe.jpg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_91e22c683c29402cbabf4ea79f7a2a9d~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_122,h_69,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_91e22c683c29402cbabf4ea79f7a2a9d~mv2.jpg)\n\n### Café\n\nUP TO 140 GUESTS\n\nImpress your guests with panoramic views of the Capitol East neighborhood from our 3rd Floor Cafe. With seating for up to 140, it's the perfect space for your next event.\n\nINQUIRE NOW\n\n### Patio\n\nUP TO 60 GUESTS\n\nEnjoy in the outdoors in style with our stunning patio space from our 3rd Floor. With seating for up to 60, it's the perfect space for entertaining and evening toasts.\n\nINQUIRE NOW\n\n![startingblock-madison-am-fam-cafe.jpg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_91e22c683c29402cbabf4ea79f7a2a9d~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_122,h_69,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_91e22c683c29402cbabf4ea79f7a2a9d~mv2.jpg)", "char_len": 1991, "id": 17, "source": "StartingBlock Madison", "type": "static_html", "category": "accelerator", "url": "https://www.startingblockmadison.org/"}
{"chunk_id": "starting-block-madison::40", "doc_slug": "starting-block-madison", "chunk_index": 40, "text": "entertaining and evening toasts.\n\nINQUIRE NOW\n\n![startingblock-madison-am-fam-cafe.jpg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_91e22c683c29402cbabf4ea79f7a2a9d~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_122,h_69,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_91e22c683c29402cbabf4ea79f7a2a9d~mv2.jpg)\n\n## [page] https://www.startingblockmadison.org/community\n\n![VI6A3073-scaled.jpg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_c8b54027d51541369572d536a3a5c2a5~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_126,h_84,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_c8b54027d51541369572d536a3a5c2a5~mv2.jpg)\n\n# Find Your Community\n\n### All entrepreneurs fit at StartingBlock\n\nJOIN TODAY\n\n## Wednesday Morning Programs\n\nStartingBlock is evolving our Wednesday morning programming to better serve our diverse entrepreneurial community. Previously, we hosted One Million Cups every Wednesday. Now we're introducing a rotating monthly format that addresses different aspects of the startup journey.​\n\n​\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_aa92d258fb9b4990ac4093add8d2719d~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_151,h_140,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_aa92d258fb9b4990ac4093add8d2719d~mv2.jpg)\n\nOpen to the Community\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_d058620a41be49109a985b56e64d2168~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_140,h_140,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_d058620a41be49109a985b56e64d2168~mv2.jpg)\n\n3rd Floor Café\n\nat 9AM CT\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_59dcf556b9d249ea8ff2f2e73acce57c~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_140,h_140,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/c6ae45_59dcf556b9d249ea8ff2f2e73acce57c~mv2.jpg)\n\nCoffee Provided at All Events\n\n1ST WEDNESDAY OF THE MONTH\n\n![1 Million Cups Presentation.jpg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_017070d3da7b4490aa0d1f4beebb6525~mv2.jpg/v1/crop/x_0,y_186,w_2250,h_1087/fill/w_474,h_229,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/1%20Million%20Cups%20Presentation.jpg)\n\n##### 1 Million Cups\n\nEducating, inspiring, and connecting entrepreneurs in Madison every first Wednesday of the month.\n\nSign Up to Speak\n\n3RD WEDNESDAY OF THE MONTH", "char_len": 2136, "id": 17, "source": "StartingBlock Madison", "type": "static_html", "category": "accelerator", "url": "https://www.startingblockmadison.org/"}
{"chunk_id": "starting-block-madison::41", "doc_slug": "starting-block-madison", "chunk_index": 41, "text": "1 Million Cups\n\nEducating, inspiring, and connecting entrepreneurs in Madison every first Wednesday of the month.\n\nSign Up to Speak\n\n3RD WEDNESDAY OF THE MONTH\n\n![IMG_1666 2_edited.jpg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_b361d3bdf12347b5874cc51d83a079d5~mv2.jpg/v1/crop/x_0,y_154,w_3000,h_1089/fill/w_474,h_229,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/IMG_1666%202_edited.jpg)\n\n##### Her Network\n\nHosted by Amy Calder and Angie Ingraham, Her Network's mission is to equip women in business with resources, community, and learning opportunities to further their personal and professional development.\n\n​\n\nJoin us every 3rd Wednesday of the month from 9-10:30AM\n\nRSVP\n\n2ND WEDNESDAY OF THE MONTH\n\n![20230523_160838_1C486B.jpeg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c6ae45_92edf09c20a347dfb42950d8882fafd6~mv2.jpeg/v1/crop/x_0,y_390,w_2016,h_732/fill/w_474,h_229,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/20230523_160838_1C486B.jpeg)\n\n##### Industry Deep Dives\n\nBuild relationships with other ambitious professionals in your industry.\n\n​\n\nPast Industry Focuses\n\nAI Coding/Vibe Coding, BioHealth, Eldercare, Non-Profits, and Food & Beverage\n\nRSVP\n\n4TH WEDNESDAY OF THE MONTH\n\n![Level Set Feedback_edited.jpg](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/59b71f_72841550f89a4b658d2b71fa3aa113a1~mv2.jpg/v1/crop/x_49,y_0,w_1503,h_726/fill/w_474,h_229,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/Level%20Set%20Feedback_edited.jpg)\n\n##### Accountability Group\n\nMeet with us on the fourth Wednesday of each month to set goals, monitor key performance indicators, share progress updates, and receive collaborative support as you work toward your objectives.\n\nRSVP\n\n## Community Calendar\n\n* ![Her Network](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/59b71f_8dff2ec6575a47e1bfa7ff9a4f32ca98~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_49,h_25,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_auto/59b71f_8dff2ec6575a47e1bfa7ff9a4f32ca98~mv2.png)\n\n![Her Network](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/59b71f_8dff2ec6575a47e1bfa7ff9a4f32ca98~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_49,h_25,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_auto/59b71f_8dff2ec6575a47e1bfa7ff9a4f32ca98~mv2.png)\n\nWed, Jun 17\n\nHer Network /", "char_len": 2149, "id": 17, "source": "StartingBlock Madison", "type": "static_html", "category": "accelerator", "url": "https://www.startingblockmadison.org/"}
