{"chunk_id": "starting-block-madison::44", "doc_slug": "starting-block-madison", "chunk_index": 44, "text": "Corporate Partners\n\n### Support makes StartingBlock run!\n\nBECOME A PARTNER\n\n###### Our space and programs would not be possible without the support of many sponsors and community leaders!\n\nAbout\n\n## Corporate Partners\n\nCorporate engagement is core to the success of StartingBlock – work with our team to leverage the talents and the technologies being built by entrepreneurs in our community. We can help your organization develop its own entrepreneurial mindset and build brand awareness for your brand with our community.\n\nBECOME A PARTNER\n\nTo play, press and hold the enter key. To stop, release the enter key.\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_067dad62a5eb4efeb82aaa6f728c5bf3~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_56,h_56,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_067dad62a5eb4efeb82aaa6f728c5bf3~mv2.png)\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_5c4b61d1001643ff9cf4a6d5a6be3448~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_49,h_49,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_5c4b61d1001643ff9cf4a6d5a6be3448~mv2.png)\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_b36a2bc273774fdcb690ba0cc3f6c259~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_49,h_49,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_b36a2bc273774fdcb690ba0cc3f6c259~mv2.png)\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_ef180c0f2d9a4e9dba48db1c7c2a39a2~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_56,h_52,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_ef180c0f2d9a4e9dba48db1c7c2a39a2~mv2.png)\n\n![Wisconsin Economic Development Corporation](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_0a777dd169ec4f7dadda7aecaf605bcc~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_147,h_147,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_0a777dd169ec4f7dadda7aecaf605bcc~mv2.jpg)\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_067dad62a5eb4efeb82aaa6f728c5bf3~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_56,h_56,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_067dad62a5eb4efeb82aaa6f728c5bf3~mv2.png)\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_5c4b61d1001643ff9cf4a6d5a6be3448~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_49,h_49,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_5c4b61d1001643ff9cf4a6d5a6be3448~mv2.png)", "char_len": 2148, "id": 17, "source": "StartingBlock Madison", "type": "static_html", "category": "accelerator", "url": "https://www.startingblockmadison.org/"}
