q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_a032202b9fad460ba8457a016de07b11~mv2.png)\n\n![Winnow Fund Logo](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_bba03db536f04aacb6b1df07d93feb88~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_49,h_49,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_bba03db536f04aacb6b1df07d93feb88~mv2.png)\n\n## Community Partners", "char_len": 2222, "id": 17, "source": "StartingBlock Madison", "type": "static_html", "category": "accelerator", "url": "https://www.startingblockmadison.org/"}
{"chunk_id": "starting-block-madison::46", "doc_slug": "starting-block-madison", "chunk_index": 46, "text": "Fund Logo](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_bba03db536f04aacb6b1df07d93feb88~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_49,h_49,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_bba03db536f04aacb6b1df07d93feb88~mv2.png)\n\n## Community Partners\n\nThe Madison region has a robust startup community. As a Community Partner, we will cross-promote your events and services.\n\nBECOME A PARTNER\n\nTo play, press and hold the enter key. To stop, release the enter key.\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_37281e7bbf654bd0b842453db5422b5f~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_125,h_125,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_37281e7bbf654bd0b842453db5422b5f~mv2.jpg)\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_05254fb81daa4dd389ceab4a0fa5ac92~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_49,h_49,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_05254fb81daa4dd389ceab4a0fa5ac92~mv2.png)\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_938d60391cc746a59bd20bbe966d0f6c~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_49,h_49,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_938d60391cc746a59bd20bbe966d0f6c~mv2.png)\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_831712d7316347e7a7414d6cb59c23f0~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_49,h_49,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_831712d7316347e7a7414d6cb59c23f0~mv2.png)\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_9aba10a2f7424c24a65d239aa224ea8d~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_75,h_50,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_9aba10a2f7424c24a65d239aa224ea8d~mv2.png)\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_e503640e0a504378aadda3c07e1cfb3e~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_49,h_49,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/397fdf_e503640e0a504378aadda3c07e1cfb3e~mv2.png)\n\n![](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/397fdf_37281e7bbf654bd0b842453db5422b5f~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_125,h_125,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0