lular-logistics.png)\n\n### Cellular Logistics Inc.\n\nCardiovascular cell therapy\n\n![Centrose home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Startups_Centrose.png)\n\n### Centrose LLC\n\nPrecision therapies for advanced forms of cancer\n\n![Chess Health home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Startups_CHESSHealth.png)\n\n### CHESS Mobile Health Inc.\n\nOngoing mobile support and relapse prevention for people recovering from alcohol-use disorders", "char_len": 2286, "id": 5, "source": "WARF - Starting a Company", "type": "static_html", "category": "legal", "url": "https://www.warf.org/commercialize/starting-a-company/"}
{"chunk_id": "warf-starting-a-company::77", "doc_slug": "warf-starting-a-company", "chunk_index": 77, "text": "Centrose LLC\n\nPrecision therapies for advanced forms of cancer\n\n![Chess Health home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Startups_CHESSHealth.png)\n\n### CHESS Mobile Health Inc.\n\nOngoing mobile support and relapse prevention for people recovering from alcohol-use disorders\n\n![Cynata Therapeutics home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Startups_Cynata.png)\n\n### Cynata Incorporated\n\nMesenchymal stem cells (MSCs) for therapeutic use\n\n![Design Therapeutics home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Startups_DesignTherapeudics.png)\n\n### Design Therapeutics LLC\n\nTherapy development for degenerative disorders caused by nucleotide repeat expansions\n\n![Dianomi Therapeutics home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Startups_DIANOMI.png)\n\n### Dianomi Therapeutics Inc.\n\nMineral Coated Microparticle technology treatment targeting autoimmune diseases\n\n![EndSulin home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Startups_Endsulin.png)\n\n### Endsulin\n\n![](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/FieldProphetlogo1-scaled.jpg)\n\n### Field Prophet\n\nWeather risk prediction tools for farmers\n\n![Flue Gen home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Startups_FluGen.jpg)\n\n### FluGen Inc.\n\nInfluenza vaccines\n\n![](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Galilei-Biosciences.png)\n\n### Galilei BioSciences Inc.\n\nDeveloping sirtuin-activating therapeutics for neuroprotective indications\n\n![GlucanBio home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Startups_glucanbio.png)\n\n### Glucan Biorenewables LLC\n\nEconomical biomass conversion\n\n![Green Bay Tech home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Startups_GreenBayTech.png)\n\n### GreenBay Technologies Inc.\n\nArtificial intelligence and machine learning for data management\n\n![Gregor Diagnostics home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Startups_gregor.png)\n\n### Gregor Diagnostics Inc.\n\nHighly accurate tests to aid in the diagnosis and monitoring of prostate cancer\n\n![](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/HappyScratch_web.png)\n\n### Happy Scratch\n\nReduces itching caused by food and seasonal allergies in dogs and cats\n\n![Hello! Loom home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Startups_HelloLoom.png)", "char_len": 2267, "id": 5, "source": "WARF - Starting a Company", "type": "static_html", "category": "legal", "url": "https://www.warf.org/commercialize/starting-a-company/"}
