ncer treatments to patients\n\n![MEI home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Startups_MedicalEngineeringInnovationsLogo.jpg)\n\n### Medical Engineering Innovations Inc.\n\nMore effective tools for liver surgery and localized cancer treatment by heat\n\n![Microfabrica home](https://www.warf.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Startups_microfabrica.png)\n\n### Microfabrica Inc.\n\nHigh volume production microscale additive manufacturing platform", "char_len": 2273, "id": 5, "source": "WARF - Starting a Company", "type": "static_html", "category": "legal", "url": "https://www.warf.org/commercialize/starting-a-company/"}
